{"tid":2095994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日本就香港問題與美國保持距離，謹慎看待制裁","createTime":"2020-07-06T01:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T01:47:20.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"422f214a63997a386b697acd97f36e8debf60a84","tid":2095994,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"【共同社7月4日電】圍繞如何應對制定香港維護國家安全法以強化治港的中國，日本政府力圖與各國緊密合作。有意推動各方對華採取嚴厲態度，但在制裁方面則仍持謹慎態度。由於擔心可能導致日中關係極度惡化，日本與決定實施制裁的美國保持距離。<br />\n<br />\n  政府消息人士4日就對華制裁給出否定看法，認為此舉並不現實，稱&ldquo;日中關係轉冷，日本經濟將受嚴重影響&rdquo;。首相官邸相關人士也強調：&ldquo;美國以外各國對制裁的態度稱不上積極。&rdquo;據分析，首相安倍晉三也持謹慎姿態。<br />\n<br />\n  日本政府目前打算關注採取對華制裁措施的美方應對。官房長官菅義偉在3日的記者會上被問到日本發動制裁的可能性時，僅回答稱&ldquo;將與包括美國在內的相關國家合作，要求中國採取恰當應對&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  但從防備國際形勢各種展開的觀點出發，將不把制裁排除出未來的選項並推進研究。具體而言，限制向中國當局人士等發放簽證等措施有被談論。<br />\n<br />\n  在與各國的合作方面，包括日美在內的七國集團（G7）能否一致發出比迄今更強的訊息成為焦點。面向考慮8月下旬至9月初在美國舉行的G7峰會，日本政府將正式與參加國開展意見調整。<br />\n<br />\n  G7外長6月中旬發表聯合聲明對中國表示&ldquo;嚴重關切&rdquo;，但沒能阻止香港國安法的施行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/6d543a942662--.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F07%2F6d543a942662--.html&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=dea4cbcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/07/6d543a942662--.html</a>"},{"pid":"f4601520db5f3156fbe5a5c772702896af46b129","tid":2095994,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"侵太軟弱  得把口  好難跟佢機"},{"pid":"c886645a0550bc230b7707644b69b33e1476e7a4","tid":2095994,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:04:36.000Z","msg":"TVB執到寶咁日夜強調<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f8234a0e5aecc8dfc7cfc31d525067e6d3dc21","tid":2095994,"uid":60635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"炒夠車未，次次襯星期五就出新聞抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府星期六日唔辦公唔會回應嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1fdd755ce739cc839fa2cfda77f0c3672fd078","tid":2095994,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4601520db5f3156fbe5a5c772702896af46b129","tid":2095994,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:03:54.000Z","msg":"侵太軟弱  得把口  好難跟佢機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"你條Jer就軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ef5793a552e65a9a13874dba7992cedaee2e5","tid":2095994,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:11:15.000Z","msg":"rmb"},{"pid":"a00b1660dbf1b21ea8a959a5fa7d994fdac1d06f","tid":2095994,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:13:11.000Z","msg":"《共同社》報道日本拒絕加入歐美國家批評港區國安法聯合聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2054532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2054532</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共同社<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e8af71db277d8fe64489ed6b1b3993b3572c76","tid":2095994,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"50f8234a0e5aecc8dfc7cfc31d525067e6d3dc21","tid":2095994,"uid":60635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"炒夠車未，次次襯星期五就出新聞抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府星期六日唔辦公唔會回應嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T01:13:19.000Z","msg":"依個係路透社放風的"},{"pid":"dceb6de1dfb8f53baef89bd6144b194284db79ad","tid":2095994,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32e8af71db277d8fe64489ed6b1b3993b3572c76","tid":2095994,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"50f8234a0e5aecc8dfc7cfc31d525067e6d3dc21","tid":2095994,"uid":60635,"like":3,